OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784038719
OL,3,CAndy Burnham says Hillsborough Law
OL,4,Cwill shift the balance of power
OL,6,FThe Hillsborough Law will help shift
OL,7,Fthe balance of power between the
OL,8,Fpeople and the state, prime minister-
OL,9,Fin-waiting Andy Burnham said.
OL,11,FIt will clear the Commons on Tuesday
OL,12,F14th July, after ministers agreed its
OL,13,Fduty of candour would apply to the
OL,14,Fintelligence services.
OL,16,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer said
OL,17,Fhe was "proud" to bring back the
OL,18,Flegislation, which aims to prevent
OL,19,Fcover-ups by requiring officials to be
OL,20,Ftransparent during investigations and
OL,21,Finquiries into failures by the state.
OL,26,@yD@HOUyD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
