FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784038719
OL,3,CAndy Burnham says Hillsborough Law
OL,4,Cwill shift the balance of power
OL,6,FThe law takes its name from the 1989
OL,7,Fdisaster at Hillsborough Stadium, in
OL,8,FSheffield, when 97 Liverpool fans were
OL,9,Fkilled following a crush during an FA
OL,10,FCup semi-final match.
OL,12,FFamilies of those killed were forced
OL,13,Fto fight a long campaign to get to the
OL,14,Ftruth behind the disaster in the face
OL,15,Fof obstruction by the authorities.
OL,17,FThe Prime Minister will personally
OL,18,Fsteer the legislation through its
OL,19,Ffinal Commons stages as he seeks to
OL,20,Fsecure his legacy in the closing days
OL,21,Fof his premiership.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784038719
OL,3,CAndy Burnham says Hillsborough Law
OL,4,Cwill shift the balance of power
OL,6,FHe has pushed back what is expected to
OL,7,Fbe his final Cabinet meeting to
OL,8,FWednesday in order to speak at the
OL,9,Fthird reading stage of the legislation.
OL,11,FThe law was a key promise in Labour's
OL,12,F2024 manifesto, but has been delayed
OL,13,Fby wrangling over how the measures
OL,14,Fwould apply to spies.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784038719
OL,3,CAndy Burnham says Hillsborough Law
OL,4,Cwill shift the balance of power
OL,6,FA planned debate on the legislation,
OL,7,Fformally called the Public Office
OL,8,F(Accountability) Bill, was pulled
OL,9,Fearlier this year because of the row,
OL,10,Fwith campaigners saying they could not
OL,11,Faccept a version of the law that gave
OL,12,Fthe heads of the intelligence services
OL,13,Fa veto over whether their officers
OL,14,Fcould disclose sensitive information.
OL,16,FOn Tuesday 14th July, ministers will
OL,17,Famend the Bill to bring spies within
OL,18,Fthe scope of the duty of candour, but
OL,19,Fwith a "secure process" for disclosing
OL,20,Finformation that could affect national
OL,21,Fsecurity.
OL,26,@{D@HOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784038719
OL,3,CAndy Burnham says Hillsborough Law
OL,4,Cwill shift the balance of power
OL,6,FOfficials said the changes were the
OL,7,Fresult of "months of working around
OL,8,Fthe clock with the families and
OL,9,Fcampaigners".
OL,11,FWriting in the Liverpool Echo, Mr
OL,12,FBurnham ` who will become Labour
OL,13,Fleader on Friday and prime minister on
OL,14,FMonday ` said: "We owe this moment to
OL,15,Fthe Hillsborough families.
OL,17,F"For 37 years, they refused to accept
OL,18,Fa lie. They stood firm when powerful
OL,19,Finstitutions closed ranks against them.
OL,26,@oD@KOUqD@LO]vD@POU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784038719
OL,3,CAndy Burnham says Hillsborough Law
OL,4,Cwill shift the balance of power
OL,6,F"They have shown extraordinary
OL,7,Fcourage, and because they never gave
OL,8,Fup, they will leave a legacy that
OL,9,Freaches far beyond Hillsborough. They
OL,10,Fare helping to reshape the
OL,11,Frelationship between the public and
OL,12,Fthe state for generations to come."
OL,14,FIn a sign of how he hopes to change
OL,15,Fthe country when he enters No 10, Mr
OL,16,FBurnham added: "The lesson of
OL,17,FHillsborough goes beyond introducing a
OL,18,Fduty of candour.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@cO]xD@POU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784038719
OL,3,CAndy Burnham says Hillsborough Law
OL,4,Cwill shift the balance of power
OL,6,F"It asks us what kind of country we
OL,7,Fwant to be. One where power is
OL,8,Fconcentrated in distant institutions,
OL,9,For one where it is shared more fairly
OL,10,Fwith the people and places those
OL,11,Finstitutions are meant to serve.
OL,13,F"If an entire city could be ignored
OL,14,Ffor two decades while telling the
OL,15,Ftruth about the deaths of its own
OL,16,Fpeople, what other communities have
OL,17,Fgone unheard? Which voices have been
OL,18,Foverlooked simply because they lacked
OL,19,Fpower?
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784038719
OL,3,CAndy Burnham says Hillsborough Law
OL,4,Cwill shift the balance of power
OL,6,F"For me, this has always been about
OL,7,Fchanging that. It is why I believe we
OL,8,Fmust continue to redistribute power,
OL,9,Fstrengthen our towns and cities, and
OL,10,Fbuild a Britain where every community
OL,11,Fis treated with equal respect and
OL,12,Fwhere, in the face of injustice,
OL,13,Fnobody walks alone."
OL,15,FThe legislation, which will still need
OL,16,Fto go through the House of Lords, was
OL,17,Fone one of Sir Keir's key promises.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784038719
OL,3,CAndy Burnham says Hillsborough Law
OL,4,Cwill shift the balance of power
OL,6,FSir Keir said the "landmark law" was
OL,7,F"a tribute to the incredible families
OL,8,Fand campaigners who have spent decades
OL,9,Fand decades fighting to get justice
OL,10,Ffor their loved ones".
OL,12,F"They suffered unimaginable grief and
OL,13,Fnever gave up. If it wasn't for their
OL,14,Fdedication the Hillsborough Law would
OL,15,Fnever have happened," he added.
OL,17,FHillsborough Law campaigners,
OL,18,Fincluding those whose family members
OL,19,Fwere killed in the 1989 disaster,
OL,20,Fwelcomed the return of the Bill to the
OL,21,FCommons.
OL,26,@nD@SOUnD@`O]oD@AOUrD@UO]tD@AOUwD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784038719
OL,3,CAndy Burnham says Hillsborough Law
OL,4,Cwill shift the balance of power
OL,6,FIn a statement, Charlotte Hennessy,
OL,7,FSue Roberts, Steve Kelly and Margaret
OL,8,FAspinall said: "We have shown that
OL,9,Ftrue power belongs to ordinary people.
OL,11,F"We did not stay silent, we were not
OL,12,Fground down, we were not afraid to
OL,13,Fspeak truth to power.
OL,15,F"This is not just about legislation,
OL,16,Fbut about changing the way the
OL,17,Fbereaved and survivors are treated and
OL,18,Fa change in culture and it is deeply
OL,19,Fempowering knowing that this protects
OL,20,Fothers forever."
OL,26,@pD@POUsD@AOUwD@AOU|D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
